title: Ep. 849 - The Mischievous Troop - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide asks Tapu Sena not to play in the society as it is newly renovated. Tapu Sena decides to black paint the society to safeguard it from evil eye. Taarak warns Bhide to let the children play in the society lest they come up with some new mischief.

title: Ep. 850 - Abdul Is Unhappy - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Abdul listens to a lady talking badly about his shop and is depressed. He keeps feeling bad for the same. The men of Gokuldham come and cheer him up.

title: Ep. 851 - A Surprise For Abdul - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The residents realise that Abdul is going through a bad state and decide to help him. Its seen that the police arrest Abdul, but he is surprised to find out something amusing.

title: Ep. 852 - Bhide Comes To Jetha's House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha and Daya share a moment with each other when Bhide comes over. Later, Jetha gets a good news. Champaklal taunts Daya for not taking care of herself.

title: Ep. 853 - Baga And Sundar's Converse - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha reaches his shop to find out that Baga and Nattu Kaka aren't working. Later, Baga gets a text message from Sundar and is tensed. Jetha assigns a secret work to Daya.

title: Ep. 854 - Daya Finds Out The Truth - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: In her curiosity, Daya opens the boxes that Jetha tells her about. She realises that her brother had mortgaged these necklaces to Jetha. Later, she gets a call from  Bagha.

title: Ep. 855 - A Big Confusion - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha calls the goldsmith home and is ready to sell the gold ornaments. Daya tells him the truth and he is in shock. Jetha can't believe what he has heard.

title: Ep. 856 - Sundar Apologises - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha scolds Sundar for what he has done. He aplogises for the same. Jetha tells him that he would never sell his Daya's necklace come what may.

title: Ep. 857 - A Bet On Bhide's Scooter - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide and Jetha as usual get into a fight. The kids place a bet on if Bhide's scooter will start or no. They make fun of him and he becomes a laughing stock.

title: Ep. 858 - Popatlal And Champaklal Take A Stand - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu challenges the other kids for a cricket. They have their food and come and find out that the ground is locked down and nobody is allowed. They inform the same to Popatlal And Champaklal. They decide to help them.

title: Ep. 859 - No Backing Out - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Champaklal goes to Gada electronics. He thinks of calling a lawyer to tackle the situation. He doesn't step back in fighting for the right thing.

title: Ep. 860 - Jetha's Request To His Father - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A man who was beaten up comes and tells that he wouldn't take up the case. Jetha asks his father not to take this any further. He realises that he has too many problems in his life now.

title: Ep. 861 - Will The Issue Be Resolved? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha, Popatlal, Tapu and Champak go the person who owns the land. They ask him not to build any mall on this land. Jetha asks him to forget everything that has happened to save them from any sort of trouble.

title: Ep. 862 - Is Trouble Awaiting? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The men of Gokuldham have no other option other than just going to the goon's office and teach him a lesson. They all land up there thinking it as a solution.

title: Ep. 863 - Concerned Families - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After the mne of Gokuldham are released from jail, they are asked to withdraw the case by their respective wives. None of them are ready to do so.
